{"tid":2279831,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲被控 押後至明年1月中再提堂 續准以原有的1,000元保釋","createTime":"2020-11-10T05:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T05:53:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3671709c4195e375d0cab14be38c7f8ada71d2e1","tid":2279831,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WHG1P772gTNBfKiZWA2F1IFlg7g=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QG2GDXULKFGPZLTLKITGA3LF4I.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWHG1P772gTNBfKiZWA2F1IFlg7g%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQG2GDXULKFGPZLTLKITGA3LF4I.JPG&h=bde0cb3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港電台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲早前就7.21調查報道進行查冊，因而被捕，遭拘控兩項明知而作出在要項上虛假陳述罪，案件今於粉嶺裁判法院提堂。控方申請暫時毋須答辯，押後以等待警方完成調查，包括向運輸署索取資料；又因被告在網上進行查冊，故警方須進行電子認證。主任裁判官蘇文隆押後案件至明年1月14日再訊，續准被告以原有的1,000元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n控方不反對被告以原有條件繼續保釋。辯方律師陳信忻不反對押後案件。<br />\n<br />\n被告蔡玉玲（37歲），被控兩項明知而作出在要項上虛假的陳述罪，違反香港法例第374章《道路交通條例》第111(3)(a)條，指被告分別於今年5月17日及6月10日在香港為取得同一輛私家車的車輛登記細節證明書，明知而作出在要項上虛假的陳述，表示申請證明書以作與交通及運輸事宜有關的用途，即進行法律程序和買賣車輛以外的其他有關交通及運輸事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/SG3YNWNOAFHT3KBXZNITMAC7BU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FSG3YNWNOAFHT3KBXZNITMAC7BU%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=0b3f6772\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FSG3YNWNOAFHT3KBXZNITMAC7BU%2F&h=113df2a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/SG3YNWNOAFHT3KBXZNITMAC7BU/</a>"},{"pid":"0e7c177734e293d3cbb3db245578cc55b668733d","tid":2279831,"uid":218729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:16:21.000Z","msg":"張表格根本唔比你填其他嘢"},{"pid":"bb9bbd659bd19395e44f13c438b19118e2342845","tid":2279831,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b9ff85c9b6f2aee3a9f4f97c9aba0e19a7be56","tid":2279831,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"280dd8bf970d045dcbe3a26ec9d81c636f150588","tid":2279831,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f6824383c8bfa292147521a890c9e6a4e0274a","tid":2279831,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54b33e004754be4d55c66e4dd1d142ea750f397","tid":2279831,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}